en-us: Have you tested positive for COVID-19?
en-zw: Have you tested positive for COVID-19?

en-us: Have you had known exposure to COVID-19 in the past 14 days?
en-zw: Have you had known exposure to COVID-19 in the past 14 days?
es-es: ¿Usted sabe con seguridad que ha estado expuesto al COVID-19 en los últimos 14 días?

en-us: Have you either developed new symptoms or are your existing symptoms getting worse?
en-zw: Have you either developed new symptoms or are your existing symptoms getting worse?
es-es: ¿Tiene síntomas nuevos o los síntomas que ya tenía se están poniendo peor?

en-us: Have you had any of the following:- Fever greater than 100.4F (38.0C) for more than 24 hours- Cough- Trouble breathing- Body aches- Chills- Diarrhea- Headache- Runny nose- Sore throat
en-zw: Have you had any of the following:- Fever greater than 100.4F (38.0C) for more than 24 hours- Cough- Trouble breathing- Body aches- Chills- Diarrhea- Headache- Runny nose- Sore throat
es-es: ¿Ha tenido algo de lo siguiente?- Fiebre de más de 100.4 F (38.0 °C) por más de 24 horas- Tos- Dificultad para respirar- Dolor de cuerpo- Escalofríos- Diarrea- Dolor de cabeza- Catarro, gripa- Dolor de garganta

en-us: Are you experiencing any of the following:- Fever greater than 100.4F (38.0C) that has lasted more than 24 hours- Cough- Trouble breathing
en-zw: Are you experiencing any of the following:- Fever greater than 100.4F (38.0C) that has lasted more than 24 hours- Cough- Trouble breathing
es-es: ¿En este momento tiene algo de lo siguiente?- Fiebre de más de 100.4 F (38.0 °C)  por más de 24 horas- Tos- Dificultad para respirar

en-us: Have you traveled to one of the [Centers for Disease Control and Prevention’s high-risk countries](https://wwwnc.cdc.gov/travel/notices) within the last 14 days?
en-zw: Have you traveled to one of the [Centers for Disease Control and Prevention’s high-risk countries](https://wwwnc.cdc.gov/travel/notices) within the last 14 days?
es-es: ¿Ha viajado a alguno de los países [considerados de alto riesgo por los Centros para el Control y la Prevención de Enfermedades](https://wwwnc.cdc.gov/travel/notices) en los últimos 14 días?

en-us: If you are an existing patient, send your provider a message using [MyAdvocateAurora](https://myadvocateaurora.org/chart/) or the [LiveWell app](https://www.advocateaurorahealth.org/livewell).
en-zw: If you are an existing patient, send your provider a message using [MyAdvocateAurora](https://myadvocateaurora.org/chart/) or the [LiveWell app](https://www.advocateaurorahealth.org/livewell).
es-es: Si usted es paciente actualmente, envíe un mensaje a su proveedor usando [MyAdvocateAurora](https://myadvocateaurora.org/chart/) o la aplicación [LiveWell app](https://www.advocateaurorahealth.org/livewell).

en-us: We recommend that you schedule a video visit with one of our providers through our LiveWell app.
en-zw: We recommend that you schedule a video visit with one of our providers through our LiveWell app.
es-es: Llame al 1 (866) 443-2584 para hablar con uno de los miembros de nuestro equipo, quien le preguntará sobre sus síntomas y determinará la mejor manera de proceder con la atención.

en-us: Visit your nearest emergency department for further evaluation.
en-zw: Visit your nearest emergency department for further evaluation.
es-es: Vaya a la sala de emergencias más cercana para evaluaciones adicionales.

en-us: Has the child tested positive for COVID-19?

en-zw: Does the child have any of the following:- Fever greater than 100.4F (38.0C) for more than 24 hours- Cough- Trouble breathing- Appears ill or weak- Body aches- Chills- Diarrhea- Headache- Runny nose- Sore throat

en-us: Is the child younger than 3 months of age?

en-zw: If your child is an existing patient, send your child’s provider a message using [MyAdvocateAurora](https://myadvocateaurora.org/chart/) or the [LiveWell app](https://www.advocateaurorahealth.org/livewell).

en-us: Visit your nearest emergency department for further evaluation.
en-zw: Visit your nearest emergency department for further evaluation.
es-es: Vaya a la sala de emergencias más cercana para evaluaciones adicionales.

en-us: Who are you doing an assessment for?
en-zw: Who are you doing an assessment for?

en-us: I understand that the Advocate Aurora Health COVID-19 Symptom Checker should never be used for urgent matters. If I am experiencing a life-threatening illness or injury or a condition I want assessed quickly, I will go to the nearest hospital emergency department and/or dial 9-1-1 for immediate attention. I will contact my Advocate Aurora Health physician by phone or seek walk-in services if I have a matter that requires medical attention and cannot wait for a routinely scheduled appointment.
en-zw: I understand that the Advocate Aurora Health COVID-19 Symptom Checker should never be used for urgent matters. If I am experiencing a life-threatening illness or injury or a condition I want assessed quickly, I will go to the nearest hospital emergency department and/or dial 9-1-1 for immediate attention. I will contact my Advocate Aurora Health physician by phone or seek walk-in services if I have a matter that requires medical attention and cannot wait for a routinely scheduled appointment.
es-es: Entiendo que el verificador de síntomas de Advocate Aurora Health COVID-19 nunca debe usarse en situaciones urgentes. Si tengo una enfermedad, una lesión o un padecimiento con riesgo de vida y deseo que me evalúen inmediatamente, acudiré al departamento de emergencias del hospital más cercano y/o llamaré al 911 para recibir atención inmediata. Me contactaré con mi médico de Advocate Aurora Health por teléfono o buscaré servicio en persona si mi situación requiere atención inmediata y no puedo esperar a una cita programada.
